<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Euro Living 歐洲安居家 | 西班牙專業安家落地服務</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.2/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root { 
            --main-gold: #c5a059; 
            --dark-blue: #1a2a3a; 
            --soft-bg: #fdfaf5; 
            --white: #ffffff;
            --text-main: #2c3e50;
            --text-muted: #7f8c8d;
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; }
        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
        body { font-family: "PingFang TC", "Microsoft JhengHei", sans-serif; margin: 0; background: var(--soft-bg); color: var(--text-main); line-height: 1.8; }

        /* --- 導覽列優化 --- */
        .navbar { 
            background: var(--white); padding: 0.8rem 2rem; display: flex; 
            justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; 
            box-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 2000; 
        }
        .logo-area { display: flex; flex-direction: column; cursor: pointer; }
        .logo-area h1 { margin: 0; color: var(--dark-blue); font-size: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: 4px; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.1; }
        .logo-area span { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--main-gold); letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 2px; }
        
        .nav-right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px; }
        .social-links { display: flex; gap: 15px; border-right: 1px solid #eee; padding-right: 20px; }
        .social-links a { color: var(--dark-blue); font-size: 1.1rem; transition: 0.3s; }
        .social-links a:hover { color: var(--main-gold); transform: translateY(-2px); }

        /* 漢堡選單：修正線條不整齊 */
        .hamburger { 
            cursor: pointer; display: flex; flex-direction: column; 
            justify-content: space-between; width: 26px; height: 16px; 
        }
        .hamburger span { display: block; width: 100%; height: 2px; background-color: var(--dark-blue); border-radius: 4px; }

        /* 全螢幕選單 */
        .nav-overlay { 
            position: fixed; top: 0; right: -100%; width: 100%; height: 100%; 
            background: rgba(26, 42, 58, 0.98); z-index: 3000; 
            display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; 
            transition: 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.77,0.2,0.05,1.0); 
        }
        .nav-overlay.active { right: 0; }
        .nav-overlay a { color: white; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1.8rem; margin: 15px 0; letter-spacing: 4px; }
        .close-btn { position: absolute; top: 25px; right: 35px; color: white; font-size: 3rem; cursor: pointer; }

        /* --- Hero: 巴塞隆納 Skyline --- */
        .hero { 
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(26, 42, 58, 0.5), rgba(26, 42, 58, 0.7)), 
                        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1583422409516-2895a77efded?q=80&w=1600&auto=format&fit=crop'); 
            background-size: cover; background-position: center; color: white; 
            padding: 180px 20px; text-align: center; min-height: 650px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
        }
        @media (min-width: 992px) { .hero { background-attachment: fixed; } }
        .hero h2 { font-size: 3.2rem; margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 3px; text-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.6); }

        /* --- 關於我們：深度內容佈局 --- */
        .section-about { padding: 100px 20px; background: var(--white); }
        .about-intro { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto 80px; text-align: center; }
        .about-intro h3 { color: var(--main-gold); font-size: 1.2rem; letter-spacing: 4px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .about-intro p { font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text-muted); }

        .about-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 50px; max-width: 1100px; margin: auto; }
        .about-item { padding: 30px; border-left: 3px solid var(--main-gold); background: var(--soft-bg); transition: 0.3s; }
        .about-item:hover { background: #fdf2e9; transform: translateX(10px); }
        .about-number { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--main-gold); font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px; display: block; }
        .about-item h4 { margin: 0 0 15px; color: var(--dark-blue); font-size: 1.4rem; }
        .about-item ul { padding-left: 20px; margin: 0; color: var(--text-muted); }
        .highlight-box { grid-column: 1 / -1; background: var(--dark-blue); color: white; padding: 50px; border-radius: 20px; text-align: center; margin-top: 40px; }
        .highlight-box h4 { color: var(--main-gold); font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 20px; }

        .cta-btn { display: inline-block; background: var(--main-gold); color: white; padding: 20px 60px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 30px; transition: 0.3s; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.4); }
        .cta-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); background: #b08d4a; }

        footer { background: #f0f2f5; text-align: center; padding: 60px 20px; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav class="navbar">
    <div class="logo-area" onclick="window.scrollTo(0,0)">
        <h1>EURO LIVING</h1>
        <span>Relocation & Lifestyle Expert</span>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-right">
        <div class="social-links">
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/1BBk4G2nhR/" target="_blank"><i class="fa-brands fa-facebook-f"></i></a>
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/euroliving.tw" target="_blank"><i class="fa-brands fa-instagram"></i></a>
            <a href="https://www.threads.net/@euroliving.tw" target="_blank"><i class="fa-brands fa-threads"></i></a>
        </div>
        <div class="hamburger" id="hamburgerBtn">
            <span></span><span></span><span></span>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>

<div id="myNav" class="nav-overlay">
    <span class="close-btn" id="closeBtn">&times;</span>
    <a href="#about">關於我們</a>
    <a href="#whyus">為什麼選我們</a>
    <a href="#contact">預約諮詢</a>
</div>

<section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
        <h2>讓您的西班牙生活輕鬆落地</h2>
        <p>專業、誠信、在地的一站式安家支援服務</p>
        <a href="#about" class="cta-btn">了解我們的故事</a>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- 關於我們區塊 -->
<section class="section-about" id="about">
    <div class="about-intro">
        <h3>關於我們 ABOUT US</h3>
        <h2>在陌生的地方，有人在，差別很大</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="about-grid">
        <!-- 01 -->
        <div class="about-item">
            <span class="about-number">01</span>
            <h4>我們的角色，不是代辦</h4>
            <p>每一件生活小事都可能變成壓力。我們成立的目的很單純：讓在歐洲的人，不需要一個人面對這些事情。</p>
        </div>
        <!-- 02 -->
        <div class="about-item">
            <span class="about-number">02</span>
            <h4>在地支援，而非零散服務</h4>
            <p>我們是長期存在的在地團隊。不是幫你做所有事，而是讓你做得更安心。</p>
        </div>
        <!-- 03 -->
        <div class="about-item">
            <span class="about-number">03</span>
            <h4>我們服務誰</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>初到歐洲生活的人</li>
                <li>長期旅居、缺乏支援的人</li>
                <li>即將前往遊留學的學生</li>
                <li>特別是：人不在歐洲，但牽掛在歐洲的人</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <!-- 04 -->
        <div class="about-item">
            <span class="about-number">04</span>
            <h4>我們在做的事情</h4>
            <p>從安頓協助到行政流程陪同。有我們在，會更快、更安心、少走很多彎路。</p>
        </div>
        <!-- 05 -->
        <div class="about-item">
            <span class="about-number">05</span>
            <h4>我們的不同</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>穩定在地，而非臨時協助</li>
                <li>理解華人文化與家庭需求</li>
                <li>以「關係」為基礎，真的找得到人</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <!-- 06 -->
        <div class="about-item">
            <span class="about-number">06</span>
            <h4>我們相信的事</h4>
            <p>最重要的不是資訊，而是「有人在」。當事情發生時，有人可以依靠，這就是我們存在的意義。</p>
        </div>

        <!-- 07 強調區塊 -->
        <div class="highlight-box" id="contact">
            <span class="about-number" style="color: var(--white); opacity: 0.6;">07</span>
            <h4>我們想成為什麼</h4>
            <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; max-width: 700px; margin: auto;">當您在歐洲遇到問題時，不需要搜尋、不需要焦慮。您知道有一個地方可以問，有一個人會回應。</p>
            <a href="mailto:info@euroliving.net" class="cta-btn">立即聯繫您的在地夥伴</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<footer>
    <p>&copy; 2026 Euro Living 歐洲安居家 | Barcelona & Madrid, Spain</p>
    <p>專業西班牙在地服務，做您最強大的後盾。</p>
</footer>

<script>
    const hamburgerBtn = document.getElementById('hamburgerBtn');
    const closeBtn = document.getElementById('closeBtn');
    const myNav = document.getElementById('myNav');
    const navLinks = document.querySelectorAll('.nav-overlay a');

    hamburgerBtn.addEventListener('click', () => { myNav.classList.add('active'); });
    closeBtn.addEventListener('click', () => { myNav.classList.remove('active'); });
    navLinks.forEach(link => { link.addEventListener('click', () => { myNav.classList.remove('active'); }); });
</script>

</body>
</html>
